            <subsection name="Bug">
                <ul>
                    <li>[<a href='https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PB-71'>PB-71</a>] - FacesPortlet should apply RenderKitFactory.HTML_BASIC_RENDER_KIT when default-render-kit-id is not specified</li>
