                </ul>
            </subsection>
            <subsection name="Improvement">
                <ul>
                    <li>[<a href='https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PB-74'>PB-74</a>] - Safe creation of context in GenericVelocityPortlet for JS2's new feature, auto-dispatching for edit_defaults mode.</li>
                    <li>[<a href='https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PB-75'>PB-75</a>] - GroovyPortlet need to support Jetspeed's new feature, auto-dispatching for edit_defaults mode option.</li>
                </ul>
